# Enforce LF line endings across the repo on all platforms.
# Works with core.autocrlf=true on Windows: files are stored as LF in the
# index and checked out as LF in the working tree, so local tooling (Biome,
# Prettier, etc.) matches what CI sees on Linux runners.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files that should never be modified.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
